cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use Tracebook in research or engineering work, please cite this software."
type: software
title: "Tracebook: Matching-Engine Conformance Testing and Reproducible Failure Analysis"
abstract: >-
  Tracebook runs deterministic order-lifecycle traces through an inspectable
  reference engine and an external matching engine, compares semantic outcomes,
  localizes the first divergence, and reduces failures to reproducible CI
  regressions.
authors:
